Package com.rb.nonbiz.collections

Class OneOf3<T1,​T2,​T3>

java.lang.Object
com.rb.nonbiz.collections.OneOf3<T1,​T2,​T3>
public class OneOf3<T1,​T2,​T3>
extends java.lang.Object
A mini-collection that represents a triple where exactly one of the objects exists, i.e. we're not allowed to have 0, 2, or 3 of them be specified.

This is a generalization of Either, but we won't rename Either to OneOf2, because it is fairly widely used in the code and is therefore already established.
